        <div class="col-xs-6">
            <p>我的H币余额：<span class="text-lg text-green">@ViewBag.MyAccount.User.UserExtend.HCoin</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;我的现金余额：<span class="text-lg text-green">@ViewBag.MyAccount.User.UserExtend.RmbCoin</span> <a href="/account/moneylog">资金管理</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-xs-6">
            <div class="text-right">                
